==健康素食==
方大同自幼素食，并两度被亞洲善待動物組織<ref>[http://china.petaasiapacific.com/index.asp 亚洲善待动物组织] {{Wayback|url=http://china.petaasiapacific.com/index.asp |date=20120716055208 }}</ref>授予“亚洲最性感素食男艺人”的称号。2010年前是奶蛋素食者。方大同表示：“由於长期素食，我很少生病。为了健康，应该远离乳制品。”<ref>{{cite web|title=谁是最性感素食名人？|url=http://china.petaasiapacific.com/featureSexiestVegetarianCeleb2012.asp?utm_source=Media%2BRelease&utm_medium=CH%2BSVC%2BNR&utm_campaign=0412%2BCH%2BSVC|publisher=亚洲善待动物组织|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006075510/http://china.petaasiapacific.com/featureSexiestVegetarianCeleb2012.asp?utm_source=Media%2BRelease&utm_medium=CH%2BSVC%2BNR&utm_campaign=0412%2BCH%2BSVC|archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref>

